description: Lists the access log subscriptions for the specified service network or service.

parameters.name: resourceIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID or ARN of the service network or service.

nested_items.name: items
nested_items.description: Information about the access log subscriptions.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the access log subscription.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the access log subscription was created, in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: destinationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the destination.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the access log subscription.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the access log subscription was last updated, in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: resourceArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the service or service network.

nested_items.name: resourceId
nested_items.description: The ID of the service or service network.

nested_items.name: serviceNetworkLogType
nested_items.description: Log type of the service network.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token for the next page of results.
